<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
  <head>
    <meta content='text/html; charset=UTF-8' http-equiv='Content-Type' />
  </head>
  <body>
    <h1>Welcome to Breakfast.com, <%= @user.name %></h1>
    <p>
      You have successfully signed up to Breakfast.com <br>
      You must activate your account by following this link: <br>
      <%= activate_url %>
      and entering your email: <br>
      <%= @user.email %> <br>
      as well as the following activation code: <br>
      <%= @user.activation_token %>
    </p>
    <p>
      To login to the site, just follow this link: <%= signin_url %>.
    </p>
    <p>Thanks for joining and have a great day!</p>
  </body>
</html>